en_8214897_0	Colombo (News 1st): The Consumer Affairs Authority notes that there is no shortage of rice in the country.
en_8214897_1	A senior official of the CAA noted that relevant reports have been obtained from island-wide Customer Service Officers.
en_8214897_2	He also said that large scale rice mill owners have sent rice stocks to rice shortage areas.
en_8214897_3	Meanwhile, search operation continues to nab traders who sell rice beyond the control price.
